  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The mighty Dahlan Empire is falling, ravaged by a mysterious plague and internal unrest. While surviving powers and invading nations fight among themselves, adventurers and mercenaries venture inside this land full of opportunities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your character and embark on an epic journey, enjoying complete freedom in a true sandbox RPG experience. Everything you do affects the world and its people. All important events are recorded. All characters will interpret what’s happening based on their morality and their faction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game’s narrative changes based on your choices and the people you help, making your adventure in the world of Dustgrave unique to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393370/extras/fd2efd66b3feb1a07fae320a2ea3a767.webp?t=1767363863\" width=800 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393370/extras/9188c248f803e834492617983142ff2a.poster.avif?t=1767363863\" width=800 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393370/extras/9188c248f803e834492617983142ff2a.webm?t=1767363863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393370/extras/9188c248f803e834492617983142ff2a.mp4?t=1767363863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The characters will judge your good and evil deeds based on their personality or faction. You may be a robber, despised by common folk, but selling stolen goods could kick-start your career in the local crime groups!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393370/extras/4eba2e8ae69ce42dd14c5ba7827eb7d2.webp?t=1767363863\" width=800 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393370/extras/ccbb87ad78842d068cbe417683b2df6d.poster.avif?t=1767363863\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393370/extras/ccbb87ad78842d068cbe417683b2df6d.webm?t=1767363863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393370/extras/ccbb87ad78842d068cbe417683b2df6d.mp4?t=1767363863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Factions will fight against each other, pillaging and conquering settlements. Some may become major players in the area. Others may be destroyed forever.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393370/extras/03bfc917ebc45f327e4f025c5fb59113.webp?t=1767363863\" width=800 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393370/extras/8eb6c79996f0223d3d97ad29d4c22fa4.poster.avif?t=1767363863\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393370/extras/8eb6c79996f0223d3d97ad29d4c22fa4.webm?t=1767363863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393370/extras/8eb6c79996f0223d3d97ad29d4c22fa4.mp4?t=1767363863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create and customize your main character in every aspect, and roleplay your alter-ego in any way you want, without any external constraint.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393370/extras/3975137861fb8db4d678897019d56026.webp?t=1767363863\" width=800 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393370/extras/cb2b92588428f3ba41331ef5f2aa6504.poster.avif?t=1767363863\" width=800 height=428 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393370/extras/cb2b92588428f3ba41331ef5f2aa6504.webm?t=1767363863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393370/extras/cb2b92588428f3ba41331ef5f2aa6504.mp4?t=1767363863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carve your own path, whether you join the Astralite clergy to fight against the heretics or steal apples from commoners! Many paths are available to you: criminal mastermind, righteous hero, ruthless mercenary, or wise archeologist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393370/extras/f69cae7287341ec9fa4b94bfe57ae23e.webp?t=1767363863\" width=800 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393370/extras/1f6b1f160a3e36c5a23cf16b5d5591fc.poster.avif?t=1767363863\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393370/extras/1f6b1f160a3e36c5a23cf16b5d5591fc.webm?t=1767363863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393370/extras/1f6b1f160a3e36c5a23cf16b5d5591fc.mp4?t=1767363863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Smash your enemies with a complex yet accessible turn-based combat system! Thanks to a unique combat system you can experiment with Skills and Items combinations. Find overpowered combos and destroy everyone stupid enough to fight you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393370/extras/a2326ea6b924ebda12273d534d4f026c.webp?t=1767363863\" width=800 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393370/extras/94515f22a03a6d9ad004cb8f783dd82f.poster.avif?t=1767363863\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393370/extras/94515f22a03a6d9ad004cb8f783dd82f.webm?t=1767363863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393370/extras/94515f22a03a6d9ad004cb8f783dd82f.mp4?t=1767363863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use a stealth system to do anything you want. Steal something? Check! Assassinate someone? Check! Watch people sleep? Check! Pickpocket Marco during a quest and use his keys to rob his house while he's still kidnapped? Quite specific, but still doable! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The mighty Dahlan Empire is falling, ravaged by a mysterious plague and internal unrest. While surviving powers and invading nations fight among themselves, adventurers and mercenaries venture inside this land full of opportunities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your character and embark on an epic journey, enjoying complete freedom in a true sandbox RPG experience. Everything you do affects the world and its people. All important events are recorded. All characters will interpret what’s happening based on their morality and their faction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game’s narrative changes based on your choices and the people you help, making your adventure in the world of Dustgrave unique to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393370/extras/fd2efd66b3feb1a07fae320a2ea3a767.webp?t=1767363863\" width=800 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393370/extras/9188c248f803e834492617983142ff2a.poster.avif?t=1767363863\" width=800 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393370/extras/9188c248f803e834492617983142ff2a.webm?t=1767363863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393370/extras/9188c248f803e834492617983142ff2a.mp4?t=1767363863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The characters will judge your good and evil deeds based on their personality or faction. You may be a robber, despised by common folk, but selling stolen goods could kick-start your career in the local cri